productName: Pyunkang Yul Cleansing Foam
Google descriptions: A gentle cleanser that deeply cleanses without drying or irritating the skin. The star ingredient, Saposhnikovia Divaricata Root Extract, is rich in Vitamin B, beta carotene and other mineral ingredients to calm troubled skin. Elastic foam for a dreamy cleansing experience! The formula with a stretchy consistency absorbs skin waste and cleans it thoroughly. A gentle but mighty cleansing foam made with ledebouriella seseloides extract that deliver highly effective cleansing with lots of delightful bubbles.
incide_ingredients: Saposhnikovia Divaricata Root Extract, Glycerin, Myristic Acid, Lauric Acid, Potassium Hydroxide, Stearic Acid, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Beeswax, Glyceryl Stearate, [more]Peg-100 Stearate, Glycol Distearate, Lauramide Dea, Glyceryl Stearate Se, Sodium Polyacrylate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Fragrance[less]
incide_enDescription: A gentle but mighty cleansing foam made with ledebouriella seseloides extract that deliver highly effective cleansing with lots of delightful bubbles. The stretchy consistency of Pyunkang Cleansing Foam adheres to dirt and oil trapped in pores, and removes them leaving skin feeling clean and fresh without drying.
